{"title":"春天的赞歌","authors":["成葆德"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的赞歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成葆德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是一道阴云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掠过祖国的蓝天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是一个恶魔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然降临在人间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非典！非典！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场重大的灾难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把中国人民考验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场没有硝烟的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正把中华民族精神磨炼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中南海正在开会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国务院作出决策；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个前所未有的号召啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个前所未有的动员！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从中国军事医学科学院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到南国防疫研究所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“万众一心，众志成城”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是民族的誓词，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是必胜的预言！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲上去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步伐是那样平静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步履是那样轻捷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像农民走进农田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像工人走进车间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像战士走进战壕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像雄鹰飞向蓝天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从院士到护士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北国到江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像萧萧易水边的壮士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有回顾和退缩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶欣、邓练贤、梁世奎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“男儿到死心如铁”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姜素椿、钟南山、赵世慧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“看试手，补天裂！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有多少人啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都走在他们中间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛已经非常遥远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，我看见了那动人的画面："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白求恩弯曲的腰背，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正站在手术台前；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林巧稚瘦弱的身躯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正为母亲分娩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南丁格尔的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时在队伍中闪现；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希波克拉底的誓言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在春风中回旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在草长莺飞的三月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个民族在发出共鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个民族在告诉世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远唱着春天的故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远唱着英雄的赞歌！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":16,"page_end":16}